    "Background": {
      "text": "Formerly known known as \"pneumocystis\ncarinii\npneumonia\" (i.e. \"PCP\")\nAn atypical fungus\n[1]\nMost common opportunistic infection in\nAIDS\npatients\nMost common identifiable cause of death",
      "subsections": {
        "Risk_factors": {
          "text": "CD4 < 200\nImmunosuppressive medications\nCancer\nPrimary immunodeficiencies\nSevere malnutrition",
          "tables": []
